works.description: The Turntable iPhone Dock is undeniably one of the coolest and sexiest iPhone docks we’ve ever seen. The only thing we didn’t like about it is that fact that it’s just a concept for now. Designed by Olivier Meynard, the Turntable iPhone Dock aims to combine two objects characteristic of their time to offer something that could be seen as a perfect union of the past and the present. If you are one of those individuals who thinks the best way to listen to music is on a turntable, this iPhone Dock seems to be a great option.
